Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Shimogamo Shrine is located {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the triangular area surrounded\Nby the Takano and Kamo rivers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although there are mountains of\Nshrines with noble lineages in Kyoto,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shimogamo Shrine is one of the foremost{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}among the ones that existed\Nprior to the Heian period.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though scores of visitors\Ngo there throughout the year{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to receive matchmaking and all\Nkinds of other blessings from the gods,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}few know that a small ramen cart\Nappears in the vicinity each and every night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's called Neko Ramen.\N{\i0}[{\i1}neko{\i0}: cat]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rumor is it uses\Nactual cats to makes the broth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but whether that's true or\Nnot cannot be ascertained.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the taste is unmatched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a person of Shimogamo Yuusuisou, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:01:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact I am a resident of Shimogamo Yuusuisou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shimogamo Yuusuisou is a boarding\Nhouse behind Eizan Demachiyanagi Station,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it's apparently exactly the same as it\Nwas since it was rebuilt after it disappeared{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}during the violence of the final\Ndays of the Tokugawa shogunate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it weren't for the light leaking out the\Nwindows, it would be no different than ruins,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when I visited there at the introduction\Nof the University Co-op at the start of school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no wonder I thought I'd\Naccidentally stumbled into Kowloon City.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, that's it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remembered that I have spotted this queer,\Ncurious fellow quite a number of times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a god of Shimogamo Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My proper name is Kamotaketsunuminokami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kamotake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamotaketsunominokamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the second time was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents' names, how you were always\Nthrowing up and making sour smells as a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your nickname during elementary school,\Nthe middle school cultural festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your fleeting first love during high school,\Nthe first time you watched an adult video,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life as a {\i1}ronin{\i0}, and your lazy,\Nidle days spent after entering college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After suffering romantic disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the club of your dreams,\Nunable to open up to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before long you started getting\Nin the way of people's path to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why have you spent these\Ntwo years in such a timid state?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Ozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept that you have had your soul\Nsomewhat dirtied by the influence of Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The past two years go rambling through\Nmy brain like swaying paper lanterns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the sacred woods of\NShimogamo Shrine, of all places,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my delicate heart was seized\Nby painful memories, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:15.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is what I wanted to scream out,\Nbut I restrained myself like a gentlemen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-None of your business.\NIt's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be Kannazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must travel to Izumo once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our job, yes, but it is quite a lot of\Nwork, and don't make light of the train fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this age we just toss everyone's proposals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the wooden box for\N"already inspected" with hardly a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet as I am a serious fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but to be deep\Nin thought, scratching my head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about which two people\Nwould be most suited for each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,almost like a matrimonial agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woe is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't follow in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fall comes we gather at Izumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and decide the relationships of man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the name Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, whom you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are you and the name Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even stupider than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a god of matchmaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am preparing to match this woman\Nyou know, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire, come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Yuusuisou, room 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This strange fellow is saying he is trying\Nto tie Akashi-san to either Ozu or me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was in high school\NI didn't participate in any club activities{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and just stayed cooped up with\Na bunch of other layabout guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and countless doors to the\Nmystical treasure that is known as{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that "rose-colored\Ncampus life" lay open before me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was half-swooned with glee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one I chose was... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:20.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cupip
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Among the raven-haired maidens\Nworking up an invigorating sweat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would begin the rally of love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is what I, a fool\Nbeyond all help, had thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first summer. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My still-as-of-yet rose-colored self was\Ncut to the quick by that which is called reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making 100 friends wouldn't be\Nso bad, or so I frivolously thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I was soon made aware of just how difficult\Ncasually getting to know other people could be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wish of a rally unfulfilled,\NI was not even able to hit back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my serves were left unreturned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried training myself to\Nbe sociable and easy-going,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I wasn't part of the\Nconversation to begin with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the time I realized I had to be sociable\Nin order to be included in the conversation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was already too late. I had\Nlost my place among the circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was then that an ominous man\Nstood beside me with a face of ill portent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some messenger from hell\Nthat only delicate little me can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry, I am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first contact with\NOzu, as well as worst contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's quite a contrast, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should mix it up over there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The place where the Kamo and Takano rivers join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}below the Shimogamo Shrine is\Nreferred to as the "Kamo River Delta,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Us, Concealed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Party Area
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is widely used as a location for parties{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from spring through summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ozu is in the same year I am. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}8 in 10 people who saw him in the\Ndark would mistake him for a youkai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the remaining two could be convinced of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eating the unhappiness of\Nothers as a topping on his rice,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's a man with seriously\Nnot a single point of praise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My soul would have surely stayed\Nunblemished were it not for having met him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you gonna turn on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop touching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the night breeze is so chilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Why does it have to be you\Nnext to me instead of a raven-haired maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look. Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0} came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the engineering department, so\Nmaybe she's designing for Birdman or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we should call it off for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get Akashi-{\i1}san {\i0}mixed up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? What happened\Nto your pride as a "Black Cupid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure I have my pride, but to someone\Nfrom the outside, this just looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let your conviction bend because\Nyou're worried about what other people think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I, who have dedicated both my\Nbody and soul, am not a person such as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not here today precisely because\Nyou bear this loneliness and isolation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones that\Nhave lost sight of reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must bring the hammer down upon those\Nwho have lost themselves among frivolous dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, without further ado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear ye, hear ye! For we\Nare the ones who hinder love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now rain the heavens down upon\Nyou merrymaking ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Id... iot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we may be idiots, but\Nyou guys should watch out for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottle rocket fireworks are for the\Npurpose of rocketing up into the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing things like holding them in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aiming them at people, or using\Nthem to bomb people over rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having a peaceful, harmonious\Nparty are quite not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your ground! Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one shallow river!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna smack you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ozu, they're not all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I had met Ozu it was just\Ncutting, cutting, and more cutting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the red threads that stretched\Nacross the circle like at Yasui-konpiragu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At these activities Ozu was ingenious,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and there were even villainous rumors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that there was no personal information\Nwe did not know and make use of,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that we would\Nscatter oil and then light fires,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and whether that was true\Nor not it was spread around{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it was an environment\Nwhere we were set up as guys{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who constantly enjoyed blazing scenes\Nof carnage here and there inside the circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like some incarnation of evil,\Na disgrace among all homo sapiens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after we were kicked out of the circle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we did not let our activities slacken,\Nwe expanded globally,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and cloaked as gods of death the evil name of\Nthe "Black Cupids" roared throughout the land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there was a maiden in love in the\Neast we'd say "Give up on that freak,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or for a man in the west worried\Nabout one-sided love we'd advise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Just give up, it's no use."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the spark of love was sprinkled in the\Nsouth, we'd immediately pour water on it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it's said love in the\Nnorth is impossible to begin with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes our victims came close to\Ndrowning us in the canals of Lake Biwa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}surrounded the boarding house, made\Nme hide in a manga cafe in Kitashirakawa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or cried at me in the middle of\NKonoe Street when I spoke too frankly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't lose, I couldn't lose,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though I was sure that losing would\Nhave let me and everyone else be happier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Except for Ozu. I could care less if he's happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I was walking, catching my breath\Nafter having run all the way to Kiyamachi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}under the overhang of someone's house{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was caught by an old woman who\Nemitted a suspiciously ghoulish aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This unplaceable aura was\Npersuasive, and thinking logically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there was no way that the\Nfortune-telling of a creature{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who emits such an aura\Ncould be anything but spot on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a face of extreme\Nimpatience... You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel that you are\Nnot blessed with a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you can make the most of your talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense your fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quickly I did tip my hat to\Nthe old woman's keen insight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To perceive my good sense and talents in\Nan instant and yet be so very unassuming,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like how a master always hides their true\Nability, it made even me forget where I was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I sense there is an\Nopportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in an excellent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always\Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab this opportunity and act on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still somewhat vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will walk this life as now, ever unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't answered anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the lost lamb?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours, Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shameless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are you popular all of sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force feeding me such a bundle of fungi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these ribbed bits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the dental hygienist\Nat the dentist I go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked totally drunk\Nand asked me out for drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've never had a young\Nlady like that stick her fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in your mouth your entire life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring me down to your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you visited the god of\Nmatchmaking at the Shimogamo Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to do it once for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what\Ndo you think of Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought I was the\Nonly person unfortunate enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to actually be able to comprehend a\Nhuman being as dumb as yourself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she might go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd much rather have a\Nbeautiful raven-haired maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes you go "whoa..." than someone who\Nis able to comprehend a person such as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're still hung up\Non being dumped by Kohinata-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were freshman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say not that name in my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become happy in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here. Akashi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}is not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that depressed look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I've wasted\Nmy perfectly lovely college life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think you're also to blame for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it doesn't\Nmatter which path you took,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd keep ending up right where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, once I met you I put all\Nmy efforts into making you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you haunt me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the way I show my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japan Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A chill went down my spine as a\Nfearsome phantom rose into my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, if you want to\Neat any more, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are pretty dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the usual place\Nfor the after-party, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Birdman Circle is camped out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't eaten meat in a\Nwhile, so if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat after a party? Do they have\Nno pride as an agricultural people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ozu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already ran out the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escape too, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's left me behind again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will handle the bill, so out the\Nback. That's what I came to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the debt, just keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Hurry and leave, I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met Akashi-san the previous year during a\Npart time job at the Shimogamo used book fair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A year younger than I, said to\Nbe in the engineering department,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and meticulously prepared at\Nanything and everything she does,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it felt like just one stare from her eyes\Nand even a shoplifter would stay their hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, really? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you do on vacations, Akashi-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I have to tell you something like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that she was not someone\Nwho was asked her weekend plans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sent her off with a fiery cheer of\N"You just keep doing things your own way!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NDon't just barge into my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just stroll on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Castella.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, so chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You giving someone something? That's rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get any lonelier than\Neating a giant Castella all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pining for a taste of a person's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He probably came to visit the person in\Nthis boarding house known as "the master."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Castella is surely the leftovers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nevertheless, just as Ozu said, a Castella\Nlike this is to be eaten together with someone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most definitely not Ozu.\NPerhaps with Akashi-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I was surprised that\NAkashi-san's name came to mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could that strange man who called himself\Na god and said he was heading out to Izumo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to decide the relationships between man\Nand woman seriously be telling the truth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kannazuki. In other words, the 10th lunar month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The myriad gods gather at Izumo,\Nleaving vacant the various lands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is quite well known. Even I know that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And among those gods there are sure to be\Nsome of suitable peculiarity. That is not the issue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The question I have often pondered is for\Nwhat reason all those gods would gather at Izumo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And written right there it says that, at Izumo,\Nafter a boisterous and outspoken argument,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the myriad gods decide the\Nrelationships between man and woman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I'd ascertained the truth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would be best for me to climb\Nthe stairs and see this god face to face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if that god from yesterday went...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ha ha, I got you good! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or something, I couldn't stand it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd surely end up cursing myself and spending\Nthe second half of my life in a right mess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if that man is really a god,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's not like I'm burning with passionate love;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would go against my beliefs {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to seek the comfort of a stranger\Nfrom this transient loneliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it not because I scorn\Nthose inexcusable students{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who cannot bear the isolation\Nand greedily seek out others{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I ran to the name of limitless\Nnotoriety as "one who hinders love"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guise of a barren,\Nagonizing, wretched life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have not I finally reaped the victory close\Nat hand from the endless number of defeats?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would I, the one who hinders love,\Nforgive myself for changing the way I live?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or will it end with me\Nproviding entertainment to the gods{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as the spider's thread to which I cling snaps?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become happy in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I don't think Akashi-san would\Nbe fooled by a freaky, finicky youkai like Ozu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like her compassion may be deep enough\Nto find a monstrous man like him intriguing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this continues and Ozu and\NAkashi-san become friendly with each other,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this will no longer be a problem of my own love;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it will become entangled\Nwith Akashi-san's future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like even my reason was crumbling\Nto pieces like the Castella before me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose to pining for love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taste is definitely unmatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately no one\Nknows where they'll set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ramen stand that\Ncomes and goes as it pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go there quite often, yes, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm hungry, if I cock my ear\NI can hear Neko Ramen's wind chime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to try eating there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I s-s-squished it... I squished it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I am not fond of moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called Mochiguman, and they\Ncome in sets of five, but I have lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not! As this earth is round,\Nyou are sure to meet once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you'd like, I'll help you search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you take me to Neko Ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promise? Ah, that's it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After careful analysis,\Nindeed over-analysis of things,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I calmly execute a perfect countermeasure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather, I'm a man who doesn't\Nhesitate to analyze to the point{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where a perfect countermeasure\Nbecomes out of reach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Analyzing the number of different\Npatterns of Akashi-san's life and my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I quickly came to a conclusion as to who\Nshould become happy, and who should not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the most vexing\Nquestion of all was whether I,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who had hindered the path\Nof love for countless people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}could at this juncture change the way I live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of the life or death struggle\Nbetween love and reason that occurred within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stumbled in my sleep-deprived\Nstate to knock on door 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give her to Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0} to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good, wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Understood, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me before 8 PM on\Nthe east side of Kamo-oohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep moving! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping on top of the bridge is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so today is Gozan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will cross this Kamo-oohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do, Akashi-{\i1}san {\i0}will\Ncome walking from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike up a conversation about\Nsomething and ask her out on a rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to\NIzumo and being a matchmaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of preparation is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but a frontal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and get out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything until now is water under the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to push forward\Ntoward that rose-colored campus life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped safely last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here for Gozan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That went well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's enough for today. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to come this far despite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}learning not even the slightest\Nbit about running the path of love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was plenty! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought something like\N"that's enough for today," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy the words of a god,\Nhurry up and run along the path of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying this was all your plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a wish to the\Ngod of matchmaking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to grab this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make a\Nserious move now, I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do my love life and you jumping\Nhave anything to do with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-{\i1}san{\i0}! The river is swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die if you jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for the fireworks? But, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, have you done some more mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You evil, good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I don't know Ozu at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't shake off the feeling of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for choosing the tennis circle "Cupid"\Nin front of that fateful clock tower.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If then I had chosen some other circle, I would\Nhave surely spent quite a different two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I could have grasped {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the mystical treasure that is known\Nas that "rose-colored campus life."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
